@AuthorizationToken = {{token}}
@baseUrl = {{host}}

@id = 1

### OBTENER PASO
GET {{baseUrl}}/pasos HTTP/1.1
Authorization: {{AuthorizationToken}}

### OBTENER PASOS
GET {{baseUrl}}/pasos/{{id}} HTTP/1.1
Authorization: {{AuthorizationToken}}

### CREAR PASO
POST {{baseUrl}}/pasos HTTP/1.1
Authorization: {{AuthorizationToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "plazo": 120,
  "prioridad": 0,
  "descripcion": "auditoria 1",
  "flujoTrabajoId": 2,
  "estadoId": 1,
  "flujoTrabajo": "/api/flujo_trabajos/2",
  "time": "H",
  "numero": 1
}

### ACTUALIZAR PASO
PUT {{baseUrl}}/pasos/41 HTTP/1.1
Authorization: {{AuthorizationToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "plazo": 87600,
  "prioridad": 0,
  "descripcion": "Auditoria 1 update",
  "flujoTrabajoId": 2,
  "estadoId": 1,
  "flujoTrabajo": "/api/flujo_trabajos/2",
  "time": "H",
  "numero": 1
}


### CONSULTAR EVENTOS
POST {{baseUrl}}/eventos/config_event?paso=1 HTTP/1.1
